WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:04.100
Previously on "Ghost Whisperer"

00:04.700 --> 00:06.400
There were 5 signs this past year:

00:06.500 --> 00:09.700
the dead dove, the bee, the dead will
walk, the return of the forgotten.

00:09.800 --> 00:15.400
The only thing that hasn't happened
is death of a loved one.

00:17.600 --> 00:18.900
She's gonna be all right.

00:19.000 --> 00:21.500
Are you trying to tell me
something about my friend?

00:21.600 --> 00:23.900
All eyes will be on you.

00:24.000 --> 00:27.900
There's a better place for you.

00:33.500 --> 00:35.500
Gabriel...

00:35.606 --> 00:36.900
what are you saying?

00:37.004 --> 00:39.001
We're blocking the light...

00:39.103 --> 00:43.308
and soon, no one's gonna get through.

00:45.000 --> 00:51.074
